@startuml DFD_Level2_AI_Chatbot_RAG
!define RECTANGLE class

skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

' External Entities
actor "Pet Owner" as Owner <<External Entity>>
rectangle "Go Backend\n(Chatbot Handler)" as GoBackend <<External Process>>
database "Groq LLM API" as Groq <<External System>>
database "FastAPI Service\n(Port 8000)" as FastAPI <<External System>>

' Level 2 Processes for AI Chatbot (4.0)
rectangle "4.1\nLoad Pet Context\n(Profile + History)" as LoadContext <<Process>>
rectangle "4.2\nGenerate Query\nEmbedding" as GenEmbedding <<Process>>
rectangle "4.3\nVector Search\n(ChromaDB k=2)" as VectorSearch <<Process>>
rectangle "4.4\nConstruct Prompt\nwith Context" as ConstructPrompt <<Process>>
rectangle "4.5\nCall LLM API\n(Groq)" as CallLLM <<Process>>
rectangle "4.6\nDetect Emergency\nKeywords" as DetectEmergency <<Process>>
rectangle "4.7\nLog Conversation\nHistory" as LogConv <<Process>>

' Data Stores
database "D2: Pets" as D2 <<Data Store>>
database "D3: Health Journals" as D3 <<Data Store>>
database "D5: Knowledge Base\n(ChromaDB Vector DB)" as D5 <<Data Store>>
database "D9: Chatbot Messages" as D9 <<Data Store>>

' Sentence Transformer Model
database "Sentence Transformer\nModel" as STModel <<ML Model>>

' Data Flows
Owner --> GoBackend : User Query + Pet ID
GoBackend --> LoadContext : HTTP Request to FastAPI\n(if service available)
GoBackend --> LoadContext : Python Exec Mode\n(if FastAPI unavailable)

LoadContext --> D2 : Get Pet Profile
D2 --> LoadContext : Breed, Age, Weight
LoadContext --> D3 : Get Medical History
D3 --> LoadContext : Health Records

LoadContext --> GenEmbedding : Contextualized Query\n(Query + Pet Info)
GenEmbedding --> STModel : Encode Query
STModel --> GenEmbedding : Query Embedding Vector

GenEmbedding --> VectorSearch : Embedding Vector
VectorSearch --> D5 : Similarity Search (k=2)
D5 --> VectorSearch : Top 2 Relevant Chunks\n+ Sources

VectorSearch --> ConstructPrompt : Knowledge Context\n+ Sources
LoadContext --> ConstructPrompt : Pet Profile + History
Owner --> ConstructPrompt : Original Query

ConstructPrompt --> FastAPI : System Prompt + Knowledge\n+ Pet Context + Query
FastAPI --> CallLLM : Execute LLM Call
CallLLM --> Groq : Formatted Prompt\n(max_tokens=384, temp=0.7)
Groq --> CallLLM : AI Response
CallLLM --> FastAPI : LLM Response
FastAPI --> DetectEmergency : Response + Query

CallLLM --> DetectEmergency : LLM Response + Query
DetectEmergency --> Owner : Emergency Alert\n(if critical keywords found)
DetectEmergency --> LogConv : Response + Sources + Flag

LogConv --> D9 : Store Conversation\n(pet_id, query, response, sources)
LogConv --> GoBackend : Return Response + Sources + Flag
GoBackend --> Owner : AI Response + Sources\n(Normal/Emergency)

note right of GenEmbedding
  Level 2 DFD: AI Chatbot RAG System (4.0)
  
  Sub-processes:
  4.1 - Context loading (pet profile, health journal)
  4.2 - Embedding generation (Sentence Transformer all-MiniLM-L6-v2)
  4.3 - Vector similarity search (ChromaDB, k=2)
  4.4 - Prompt construction (system + knowledge + context)
  4.5 - LLM inference (Groq llama-3.3-70b-versatile)
  4.6 - Emergency detection (poisoning, bleeding, seizure, etc.)
  4.7 - Conversation logging
  
  Architecture: Hybrid (Primary + Fallback)
  - Primary: HTTP POST to FastAPI service (port 8000)
  - Fallback: Python exec mode if FastAPI unavailable
  
  Response Time: 2-3s average (8x improvement)
  ChromaDB: 281,438 veterinary documents
  Optimization: Persistent service, k=2 retrieval, max_tokens=384
end note

note bottom of D5
  ChromaDB Vector Database:
  - 281,438 veterinary documents
  - Sentence transformer embeddings
  - Metadata: source, category, relevance
  - Semantic search for retrieval
end note

note bottom of D9
  Stores conversation history:
  - pet_id, user_id, timestamp
  - query, response, sources
  - emergency_flag, rating
end note

@enduml
